                <note rend="inline" type="source">721.23/1510: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Minister in Panama</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Davis</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1933-03-31T18:00:00-05:00"
                            >March 31, 1933—6 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>38. Your 44, March 29, 3 p.m. This Government has not taken action in this
                    connection and does not expect to take any position with regard to embargoes
                    pending arrival by the League of Nations at its own decision with regard to the
                    course which should be followed by its members in relation to that subject.
                    Department does not wish to intrude in the League’s discussion of this
                    matter.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
